OL,15,FGame show. Hosted by Paul Ross. Based
OL,16,Fon the US version of the same title.
OL,17,
OL,18,FPrevious incarnations of the programme
OL,19,Faired on Channel 4 (1983 - 1984) and
OL,20,FITV (1990 - 1993). It was revived again
OL,21,Fby ITV in 2023.
